---
import PhoneMockup from "./PhoneMockup.tsx";
---

<section
  class="px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 pt-6 md:pt-10 pb-10 md:pb-14 relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-10 lg:gap-14"
  >
    <div
      class="relative z-[2] order-2 lg:order-1 text-center lg:text-left w-full lg:max-w-[540px]"
    >
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-filete-dorado/10 border border-filete-dorado/35 px-4 py-[0.35rem] mb-5 md:mb-6"
      >
        <span class="w-[7px] h-[7px] bg-filete-verde rotate-45"></span>
        <span
          class="text-[0.65rem] md:text-[0.68rem] tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-filete-dorado font-semibold"
          >Buenos Aires · CABA · AMBA</span
        >
      </div>

      <h1
        class="font-display text-[2.4rem] sm:text-[2.8rem] md:text-[3.2rem] lg:text-[3.6rem] font-black leading-[1] tracking-[-0.02em] mb-5"
      >
        Dejá de pagar<br />comisiones.<br /><span
          class="italic text-filete-dorado">El viaje es tuyo.</span
        >
      </h1>

      <p
        class="text-[0.95rem] text-filete-crema/65 leading-[1.7] max-w-[420px] mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-7 md:mb-8 font-light"
      >
        Suscripción fija mínima. Sin comisiones por viaje. El pasajero te paga
        en el acto — efectivo, Mercado Pago o tarjeta.
      </p>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center lg:justify-start"
      >
        <a
          href="/asociarse"
          class="inline-block bg-filete-rojo text-filete-crema border-[1.5px] border-filete-dorado px-7 py-[0.85rem] font-body text-[0.85rem] font-semibold tracking-[0.07em] uppercase cursor-pointer hover:bg-[#A01015] no-underline text-center"
          >Asociate ahora</a
        >
        <a
          href="/como-funciona"
          class="inline-block bg-transparent text-filete-crema border-[1.5px] border-filete-crema/25 px-7 py-[0.85rem] font-body text-[0.85rem] font-medium tracking-[0.06em] uppercase cursor-pointer hover:border-filete-dorado hover:text-filete-dorado no-underline text-center"
          >Cómo funciona</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="flex justify-center items-center relative z-[2] order-1 lg:order-2 shrink-0"
    >
      <PhoneMockup client:load />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
